{"tid":547059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【運動員悲歌】退役後下場慘淡 賣藝行乞賤賣金牌","createTime":"2018-02-01T05:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T09:07:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3310e37d497ef6365880b5172b04ab707d1686f4","tid":547059,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180131/large/1517413233_2b6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F1517413233_2b6e.jpg&h=d24391d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾冬梅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180131/large/1517413236_40c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F1517413236_40c4.jpg&h=3b714992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄒春蘭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180131/large/1517413239_b8e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F1517413239_b8e2.jpg&h=2aa8bb39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n才力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180131/large/1517413242_b184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F1517413242_b184.jpg&h=11cb2a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃成義<br />\n<br />\n中國運動員稱霸世界體壇，受盡億萬同胞喝采歡呼，但退役後，不少冠軍運動員下場慘淡，窮困潦倒，為生計在街頭賣藝行乞、公眾浴池替人搓背、擺地攤賤賣金牌，獎牌風光背後，都是說不盡的辛酸。<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\n【運動員悲歌】前體操冠軍地鐵站賣藝 被途人話係「騙子」（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2DLfb8T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DLfb8T&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=3ef5915d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2DLfb8T</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n前馬拉松名將艾冬梅手握19面金牌，因過度操練令雙腳殘疾，無法謀生，在街邊擺地攤維生，為醫病及撫養兒子更要變賣金牌。<br />\n<br />\n前世界女子舉重冠軍鄒春蘭，退役後曾在餐廳打雜，又到公眾浴池替人搓背，她揭發當年教練為了有更好成績，慫恿她們吃補藥，導致她終身不育。事件曝光後官方組織介入，資助她開洗衣店。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲男子舉重冠軍才力，曾為中國贏取無數獎牌，但因傷患被迫退役，其後在遼寧省體育運動技術學院任保安，每月收入僅1,000元人民幣（下同），但食量卻是常人的兩至三倍，還要養活家人。由於常年訓練累積一身毛病，才力最後因沒錢醫病，以致病入膏肓，33歲時不幸病死，當時家裡僅有300元積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n中國男籃名將黃成義曾是姚明的隊友，但一次腰傷斷送他的籃球夢，當時為了省錢，在小型診所動手術，結果造成癱瘓，其母後來帶他到北京求醫，悲慘遭遇曝光，獲社會關注，最後有醫院為他免費治療腰傷，讓他重新站起來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180201/57778376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57778376&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=77855edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57778376&h=818eb6e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180201/57778376</a>"},{"pid":"62cb70c30a8c20e715129cd2e3f3439285c8027f","tid":547059,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"GDP 全球數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f4c8d7353c59565e6de290a20b3eb071651ccd","tid":547059,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"中國夢呀"},{"pid":"5f88a7592f30faf503bf1c51d8dca5547f25de86","tid":547059,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"大陸就見怪不怪啦<br />\n<br />\n想知其他國家係點？"},{"pid":"1bcf27e687a01a020d5f501da0be92511166fed4","tid":547059,"uid":98386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"同condom冇分別 威就支共威曬 自己由頭到尾都受緊苦"},{"pid":"850926d99bcc2683acb5ab50ddfdf94395068948","tid":547059,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f88a7592f30faf503bf1c51d8dca5547f25de86","tid":547059,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"大陸就見怪不怪啦<br />\n<